                                                         BUSINESS QUESTION
	What is the average screen time by anxiety level group? 

                    QUERY
SELECT
  AVG(daily_screen_time)avg_screen_time,
  anxiety_level
FROM mental_health
GROUP BY anxiety_level
ORDER BY anxiety_level;

                     Insight
This research  shows that high level of  screen time does not increase anxiety in a straight line. Some users with high screen time still report moderate anxiety.

          Recommendation
We should focus less on how long people use devices, and more on what they are doing online
